Metadata-Version: 2.4
Name: AnomalousLib
Version: 0.1.1
Summary: AnomalousLib is a Python library designed for the study of anomalous diffusion. It enables dataset generation, statistical analysis, model inference, and integrated result visualization.
Author-email: Joan Massallé Richart <jmassalle@gmail.com>
License: MIT
Project-URL: Homepage, https://github.com/tu_usuario/mi_libreria
Requires-Python: >=3.12.10
Description-Content-Type: text/markdown
License-File: LICENSE
Requires-Dist: numpy>=2.2.6
Requires-Dist: scipy>=1.15.3
Requires-Dist: fbm>=0.3.0
Requires-Dist: pandas>=2.2.3
Requires-Dist: scikit-learn>=1.6.1
Requires-Dist: torch>=2.7.0
Dynamic: license-file


Para hacer pruebas en local (des de la raiz del repositorio):
python -m build
pip install .\dist\anomalouslib-0.1.0-py3-none-any.whl --force-reinstall

Para hacer update de los requirements: pip freeze > requirements.txt

No instalar una versión que no sea local a este repositorio (no?)

Para subirlo: twine upload dist/*

Activate:
en powershell: .\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1

deactivate:
en powershell : deactivate


